/* 核心职责：定义首页“此刻”页的轻量信息布局，强调问候、聚焦和流水统计三层结构。 */
.page {
  min-height: 100vh;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  padding: 28rpx 24rpx 150rpx;
  background: #ffffff;
}

.loading-wrap {
  padding-top: 220rpx;
  text-align: center;
}

.loading-text {
  font-size: 28rpx;
  color: #8e938c;
}

/* 顶部轻头部 */
.hero-wrap {
  margin-bottom: 52rpx;
}

.hero-main {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 28rpx;
}

.hero-left {
  flex: 1;
  min-width: 0;
}

.hero-title {
  font-size: 38rpx;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #222222;
  line-height: 1.42;
  margin-bottom: 14rpx;
}

.hero-quote {
  font-size: 24rpx;
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: #747870;
  margin-bottom: 8rpx;
}

.hero-from {
  font-size: 20rpx;
  color: #b5b8b1;
  line-height: 1.6;
  letter-spacing: 1rpx;
}

.hero-weather {
  width: 156rpx;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  text-align: right;
  padding-top: 6rpx;
}

.hero-weather-city {
  font-size: 20rpx;
  color: #c2c5be;
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin-bottom: 8rpx;
}

.hero-weather-temp {
  font-size: 34rpx;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: #2a2a2a;
  line-height: 1.15;
  margin-bottom: 8rpx;
}

.hero-weather-text {
  font-size: 20rpx;
  color: #c2c5be;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* 通用分区 */
.section-wrap {
  margin-bottom: 44rpx;
}

.section-title {
  font-size: 34rpx;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #222222;
  line-height: 1.35;
  margin-bottom: 8rpx;
}

.section-desc {
  font-size: 22rpx;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: #a3a79f;
  margin-bottom: 20rpx;
}

/* 今日聚焦 */
.focus-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 18rpx;
}

.focus-card {
  background: #ffffff87;
  border: 1rpx solid #f2f2ee;
  border-radius: 24rpx;
  padding: 22rpx 20rpx;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  min-height: 154rpx;
}

.focus-card:active {
  opacity: 0.88;
  transform: scale(0.985);
}

.focus-card-title {
  font-size: 20rpx;
  color: #b2b6ae;
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin-bottom: 10rpx;
}

.focus-card-value {
  font-size: 32rpx;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #222222;
  line-height: 1.35;
  margin-bottom: 10rpx;
  word-break: break-word;
}

.focus-card-desc {
  font-size: 20rpx;
  line-height: 1.75;
  color: #8a8f87;
}

/* 流水统计 */
.flow-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 18rpx;
}

.flow-card {
  background: #ffffff87;
  border: 1rpx solid #f3f3ef;
  border-radius: 24rpx;
  padding: 20rpx 20rpx 22rpx;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  min-height: 132rpx;
}

.flow-card-label {
  font-size: 20rpx;
  color: #b3b7af;
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin-bottom: 10rpx;
}

.flow-card-value {
  font-size: 28rpx;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: #2a2a2a;
  line-height: 1.35;
}

.flow-card-text {
  font-size: 20rpx;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: #8e938c;
}

/* 适当给最后一个统计卡更多可读性 */
.flow-card:last-child .flow-card-text {
  margin-top: 2rpx;
}

/* 防止底部导航压住内容 */
.section-wrap:last-of-type {
  margin-bottom: 20rpx;
}